Usage: setSnapGrid [-help] [-layer <string>] [-pitch {x y}]

-help               # Prints out the command usage
-layer <string>     # Specifies the layers for the snap grid (string, optional)
-pitch {x y}        # Specifies the pitch for the snap grid, the LEF PITCH
                    # should be multiple of the snap grid on the specific layer
                    # (point, optional)